1
00:00:58,046 --> 00:01:01,022
=Within The Grip=

2
00:01:01,022 --> 00:01:02,992
=Episode 18=

3
00:01:02,992 --> 00:01:07,014
(Have You Ever Truly Cared for Me)

4
00:01:14,159 --> 00:01:14,959
Trust?

5
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,400
Since I was a child,

6
00:01:20,319 --> 00:01:21,840
I've been in the Xuanji Pavilion.

7
00:01:23,239 --> 00:01:25,359
The first lesson we were taught was

8
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:27,760
never to trust anyone.

9
00:01:33,640 --> 00:01:34,879
When I was eight,

10
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:38,519
I shared the steamed bun
I'd won with another child.

11
00:01:39,959 --> 00:01:43,239
This scar was left
when he tried to steal my half.

12
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,319
When I was 12,

13
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:53,840
a task partner stabbed me

14
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:57,120
after I took a blow for him.

15
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,439
This scar is from taking
a Heaven task above my rank,

16
00:02:12,680 --> 00:02:14,319
where I had to fight

17
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:18,240
through the entire Earth Unit
within half an hour.

18
00:02:22,080 --> 00:02:24,240
Someone ambushed me after surrendering.

19
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:31,199
And here.

20
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,919
That's the Xuanji Pavilion.

21
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,439
I don't know who I am,

22
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:42,240
nor if I have living family.

23
00:02:43,919 --> 00:02:45,120
If they're still alive,

24
00:02:47,159 --> 00:02:49,039
why send me to the Xuanji Pavilion?

25
00:02:50,439 --> 00:02:51,840
Trustworthy people?

26
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:58,080
Even family betrays like this.

27
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:04,039
Who do you think I should trust?

28
00:03:05,199 --> 00:03:06,439
Who can I trust?

29
00:03:11,680 --> 00:03:12,479
What about you?

30
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:19,639
Have you ever truly cared for me?

31
00:03:41,792 --> 00:03:46,855
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

32
00:03:48,608 --> 00:03:54,478
♪Old dreams flow like melodious poetry♪

33
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:58,572
♪Memories fade like the passing years♪

34
00:03:58,572 --> 00:04:01,683
♪The past events leave us confused♪

35
00:04:01,683 --> 00:04:08,847
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

36
00:04:09,248 --> 00:04:14,569
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

37
00:04:15,136 --> 00:04:21,764
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

38
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:22,920
You're drunk.

39
00:04:26,528 --> 00:04:28,864
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

40
00:04:28,864 --> 00:04:35,564
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

41
00:04:35,564 --> 00:04:42,336
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

42
00:04:42,336 --> 00:04:49,472
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

43
00:04:49,472 --> 00:04:53,856
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

44
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,000
Don't leave.

45
00:04:56,480 --> 00:05:03,114
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

46
00:05:17,984 --> 00:05:23,305
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

47
00:05:23,872 --> 00:05:30,500
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

48
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:35,136
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

49
00:05:35,136 --> 00:05:37,600
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

50
00:05:37,600 --> 00:05:44,040
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

51
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:44,639
I won't leave.

52
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:51,072
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

53
00:05:51,072 --> 00:05:57,824
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

54
00:05:57,824 --> 00:06:02,592
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

55
00:06:02,592 --> 00:06:05,056
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

56
00:06:05,056 --> 00:06:11,850
♪Prosperity fades like dreams♪

57
00:06:11,850 --> 00:06:18,400
♪With nothing but memories left♪

58
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:23,759
Father.

59
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:26,639
Two Heaven tasks so close together

60
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,439
can't be a coincidence.

61
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:32,720
Can I accompany Yuluo to ensure success?

62
00:06:35,839 --> 00:06:37,279
Who said

63
00:06:38,079 --> 00:06:39,920
she's taking this task?

64
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,000
Father,

65
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:43,680
didn't you say

66
00:06:44,319 --> 00:06:45,360
once she and Zhaoxi...

67
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:49,519
Since she's a Pavilion Master candidate,

68
00:06:49,879 --> 00:06:52,199
shouldn't she handle Heaven tasks?

69
00:06:53,279 --> 00:06:55,519
There are multiple candidates.

70
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:59,279
She's not the only one.

71
00:07:28,720 --> 00:07:29,519
What about you?

72
00:07:33,040 --> 00:07:34,839
Have you ever truly cared for me?

73
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,360
Don't leave.

74
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:48,839
I won't leave.

75
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:18,300
Master.

76
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:20,240
Why did she dismiss that guard?

77
00:08:21,000 --> 00:08:22,959
Isn't she short on help now?

78
00:08:24,519 --> 00:08:28,439
Did she never trust Xuan Qing?

79
00:08:30,040 --> 00:08:33,000
Xuan Qing seemed slow-witted,

80
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:35,000
but she was loyally devoted.

81
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,399
It's not distrust.

82
00:08:38,799 --> 00:08:41,320
To her, Xuan Qing represents

83
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:45,840
a path she could've taken but didn't.

84
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,759
Maybe she let her go

85
00:08:47,960 --> 00:08:50,679
to see the outcome

86
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:52,759
of escaping that life.

87
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,279
She left overnight, heading

88
00:08:55,279 --> 00:08:57,679
toward that Jiangnan estate address
you left behind.

89
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,919
Should I...?

90
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:02,320
No. You have a more critical task.

91
00:09:02,639 --> 00:09:05,600
My wife's investigation
keeps hitting obstacles.

92
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,840
Seems her enemy has powerful influence.

93
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:10,000
Return to the palace
and investigate thoroughly.

94
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:13,399
The Heaven task?

95
00:09:15,120 --> 00:09:15,620
Yes.

96
00:09:22,752 --> 00:09:24,928
(Zuixian Building)

97
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:34,080
What brings you here today?

98
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,559
I made some pastries.

99
00:09:35,600 --> 00:09:36,480
Let me take you.

100
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,519
No need.

101
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:40,360
I do have something urgent
to discuss with you today.

102
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:44,799
Recently, I've reviewed
the pharmacy's account book.

103
00:09:45,568 --> 00:09:46,432
(Account Book)

104
00:09:48,799 --> 00:09:49,600
I discovered

105
00:09:50,639 --> 00:09:53,679
some herbs go unaccounted
for every month.

106
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:55,519
After investigating, I found

107
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:59,080
they were traced directly to you.

108
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:03,559
Interestingly, when combined,
these herbs form a toxic compound.

109
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:07,080
Long-term consumption could be lethal.

110
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:12,759
Coincidentally, I had
someone analyze the herbs

111
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:16,000
and found the symptoms

112
00:10:18,039 --> 00:10:19,960
match the family head's condition.

113
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:22,279
What?

114
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:27,200
Are you implying Father is poisoned?

115
00:10:28,000 --> 00:10:28,799
Exactly.

116
00:10:30,279 --> 00:10:31,320
Father's illness,

117
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:35,039
no, what does the poison
have to do with me?

118
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:37,679
Everyone in the Gu family
knows I specialize in poisons.

119
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:42,159
Clearly, someone's trying to frame me.

120
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:48,120
This is why you've been searching
for Physician Qin?

121
00:10:52,159 --> 00:10:53,639
How thoughtful of you.

122
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:56,679
More thoughtful than any of us.

123
00:10:58,279 --> 00:11:00,840
Xuanji, if you have nothing to hide,

124
00:11:01,399 --> 00:11:02,000
perhaps

125
00:11:02,799 --> 00:11:04,960
you'll show me what's in your sleeve.

126
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:10,360
Nothing escapes your notice, Yuluo.

127
00:11:10,679 --> 00:11:11,440
But

128
00:11:12,919 --> 00:11:14,840
my Laughing Netherworld is highly toxic.

129
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,879
Don't let it accidentally hurt you.

130
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:24,120
The entire family knows I study poisons.

131
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:25,360
As for the herbs,

132
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:29,360
why not ask Zhaoxi instead?

133
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,559
I did want to ask Zhaoxi.

134
00:11:33,320 --> 00:11:34,399
But...

135
00:11:41,320 --> 00:11:45,039
He heard I once wore
a bracelet constantly,

136
00:11:45,879 --> 00:11:48,759
so he asked about its style and sent
someone to find something similar.

137
00:11:49,519 --> 00:11:53,480
Then he learned
the bracelet contained amber

138
00:11:54,759 --> 00:11:56,000
from Nanjiang.

139
00:11:58,919 --> 00:12:00,279
If I remember correctly,

140
00:12:01,480 --> 00:12:03,759
you were there back then,

141
00:12:04,399 --> 00:12:06,039
studying medicine and poisons.

142
00:12:08,080 --> 00:12:09,519
He never expected

143
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,639
the person who delivered the amber

144
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,080
would be me.

145
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:33,080
Xuanji.

146
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,600
Playing chess alone again?

147
00:12:40,840 --> 00:12:43,080
Didn't you say
you'd return in two months?

148
00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,879
This isn't a solo game.

149
00:13:01,519 --> 00:13:02,360
This match

150
00:13:03,639 --> 00:13:04,559
isn't over yet.

151
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,919
It's your beloved?

152
00:13:20,679 --> 00:13:21,519
This is?

153
00:13:22,360 --> 00:13:24,879
Weren't you desperately
seeking premium amber?

154
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:39,600
Xuanji, you don't have to

155
00:13:40,159 --> 00:13:42,759
send it personally though.

156
00:13:43,600 --> 00:13:48,440
I'm curious to see the woman
who has caught your soul.

157
00:13:49,159 --> 00:13:50,919
I heard Father arranged your marriage.

158
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:54,320
If you want to, I can help you
escape this marriage

159
00:13:54,840 --> 00:13:56,440
to find your true love.

160
00:13:56,559 --> 00:13:57,159
Xuanji.

161
00:13:58,039 --> 00:13:58,840
You must be joking.

162
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,519
I'm completely serious.

163
00:14:02,159 --> 00:14:05,600
To me, this family is just a house.

164
00:14:05,919 --> 00:14:06,799
But you're different.

165
00:14:08,200 --> 00:14:12,480
10 years ago, no one in this family
noticed I nearly died making poison.

166
00:14:12,759 --> 00:14:14,559
Only you did and saved me.

167
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:21,120
Xuanji.

168
00:14:23,559 --> 00:14:24,360
Xuanji.

169
00:14:25,639 --> 00:14:26,440
Xuanji.

170
00:14:29,159 --> 00:14:31,039
Xuanji!

171
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:45,000
Xuanji, you'll be alright!

172
00:14:50,559 --> 00:14:53,960
To me, you're my only family.

173
00:14:55,679 --> 00:14:57,360
If anyone harms you,

174
00:14:57,960 --> 00:15:02,120
I'll make them suffer dearly,
no matter who they are.

175
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:07,039
Father isn't entirely unreasonable.

176
00:15:08,159 --> 00:15:10,960
He just doesn't know
how to connect with us.

177
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,799
Chaosheng and Wenshuang...

178
00:15:13,879 --> 00:15:16,559
Zhaoxi, you're still too naive.

179
00:15:17,200 --> 00:15:20,279
Father keeps you in this Fufeng Pavilion
under the pretext of your health.

180
00:15:20,679 --> 00:15:22,799
Who knows if it's to keep his seat?

181
00:15:24,480 --> 00:15:28,000
Everyone knows your mother
founded the Xuanji Pavilion.

182
00:15:28,879 --> 00:15:31,519
This arranged marriage is not simple.

183
00:15:32,799 --> 00:15:34,840
Chaosheng always covets
the family head position.

184
00:15:35,159 --> 00:15:37,159
Now that he knows
you're getting married,

185
00:15:38,039 --> 00:15:39,679
he won't let this go easily.

186
00:15:41,559 --> 00:15:43,759
Moreover, I've heard

187
00:15:44,039 --> 00:15:47,360
Wenshuang is close to your betrothed.

188
00:15:50,440 --> 00:15:51,320
If she

189
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,960
and Wenshuang are truly in love,

190
00:15:55,240 --> 00:15:57,159
I won't be the one to tear them apart.

191
00:15:57,919 --> 00:15:59,159
You are really...

192
00:15:59,759 --> 00:16:03,200
Always thinking of others
instead of yourself.

193
00:16:16,039 --> 00:16:17,120
You're right, Xuanji.

194
00:16:18,039 --> 00:16:20,799
When she returns, I'll ask her directly.

195
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:23,240
If she truly prefers Wenshuang,

196
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:27,799
I'll reject this marriage
even if it means defying Father.

197
00:16:28,879 --> 00:16:31,039
But what about you? Aren't you...?

198
00:16:31,039 --> 00:16:31,639
It's okay.

199
00:16:32,879 --> 00:16:33,960
I got used to it.

200
00:16:34,679 --> 00:16:36,600
Since I'm already trapped in this cage,

201
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:40,200
why drag her into it?

202
00:16:50,960 --> 00:16:54,200
I knew from the start
that man isn't Zhaoxi.

203
00:17:01,559 --> 00:17:04,039
But after noticing you were
also investigating secretly,

204
00:17:04,240 --> 00:17:06,640
didn't I share my findings with you?

205
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:08,920
That was just your test.

206
00:17:09,559 --> 00:17:10,799
And you deliberately led me

207
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,799
to investigate Chaosheng.

208
00:17:13,160 --> 00:17:16,720
If you knew, why still follow my lead
and investigate Chaosheng?

209
00:17:17,319 --> 00:17:21,240
Or did I conveniently give you a reason
to investigate him?

210
00:17:36,200 --> 00:17:37,720
You won't tell me? That's fine.

211
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:40,279
After all, you haven't disappointed me.

212
00:17:40,759 --> 00:17:44,359
You're the only one besides me
who cares about Zhaoxi's whereabouts.

213
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:48,920
I originally planned to steal
that skeleton from the yamen.

214
00:17:49,039 --> 00:17:50,640
But someone beat me to it.

215
00:17:51,599 --> 00:17:54,079
That thief was you, wasn't it?

216
00:17:57,000 --> 00:17:58,240
Was it truly...?

217
00:17:58,480 --> 00:18:02,839
Whether it was or wasn't,
the truth will surface eventually.

218
00:18:03,920 --> 00:18:06,839
But regarding the poison
the family head took,

219
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:10,119
Xuanji, your suspicion remains.

220
00:18:10,599 --> 00:18:11,960
What does that matter?

221
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:16,200
Do you think he is above suspicion
in the assassination of Zhaoxi?

222
00:18:16,799 --> 00:18:19,640
Knowing our family's turmoil,
he still asked you to marry Zhaoxi.

223
00:18:20,039 --> 00:18:23,920
Then after Zhaoxi's death, he passed
the next Heaven task to Gu Xuanwu.

224
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:28,880
Perhaps he never wanted to entrust
the Pavilion or the family to you two.

225
00:18:31,799 --> 00:18:35,079
The family head never trusts anyone.

226
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:49,839
Yuluo.

227
00:18:51,079 --> 00:18:54,680
I heard Father assigned
the Heaven task to Xuanwu.

228
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:59,200
Heaven tasks always go
to Pavilion Masters or acting Masters.

229
00:18:59,880 --> 00:19:01,200
How could he give it to Xuanwu?

230
00:19:01,880 --> 00:19:05,720
Xuanwu belongs to the Xuan Unit.
He qualifies as a candidate.

231
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:08,160
Last time, you took on
a task above your rank,

232
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:10,599
and Father promised you
the Pavilion Master position.

233
00:19:11,359 --> 00:19:13,359
The family head has his reasons.

234
00:19:14,200 --> 00:19:15,400
I don't care about reasons.

235
00:19:16,119 --> 00:19:19,319
If Father insists Xuanwu
takes on the task, I'll kill Xuanwu.

236
00:19:19,720 --> 00:19:20,680
Master Wenshuang.

237
00:19:21,599 --> 00:19:22,960
Don't act recklessly.

238
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:25,440
Recklessly?

239
00:19:27,039 --> 00:19:29,839
You know this isn't recklessness.

240
00:19:30,519 --> 00:19:33,200
Yuluo, if you want something,

241
00:19:33,440 --> 00:19:34,680
I'll obtain it for you.

242
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:39,519
I'll remove anyone blocking your path.

243
00:19:40,200 --> 00:19:42,640
Whatever Zhaoxi gives you,
I can give you too.

244
00:19:43,039 --> 00:19:45,640
What he can't do, I'll do in his place.

245
00:19:47,359 --> 00:19:47,960
Dear.

246
00:20:05,319 --> 00:20:07,599
The night wind chills.
Don't catch a cold.

247
00:20:13,039 --> 00:20:14,039
You too, Wenshuang.

248
00:20:18,240 --> 00:20:19,119
Zhaoxi.

249
00:20:22,839 --> 00:20:25,480
Is this all you can do for her?

250
00:20:27,039 --> 00:20:28,279
Zhaoxi, you must realize

251
00:20:28,920 --> 00:20:30,960
Father broke his earlier promise

252
00:20:31,519 --> 00:20:34,759
to pass the Pavilion Master title
to Yuluo upon your marriage.

253
00:20:36,279 --> 00:20:37,519
What else can you offer her?

254
00:20:38,559 --> 00:20:42,839
I'd defy Father and reclaim
the Xuanji Pavilion for her.

255
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:44,039
And you?

256
00:20:47,240 --> 00:20:49,039
Your sincerity is commendable.

257
00:20:49,279 --> 00:20:52,160
But have you truly asked what she wants?

258
00:21:27,902 --> 00:21:32,965
♪Willows sway in the twilight breeze♪

259
00:21:33,502 --> 00:21:38,823
♪Ancient alleys guard time's secrets♪

260
00:21:39,390 --> 00:21:46,018
♪Bluestones bear life's imprints♪

261
00:21:46,018 --> 00:21:50,782
♪Falling petals, endless longing♪

262
00:21:50,782 --> 00:21:53,118
♪Longing lingers within my heart♪

263
00:21:53,118 --> 00:21:59,818
♪Zither strings sigh
for the sorrow parting♪

264
00:21:59,818 --> 00:22:06,590
♪Past tales nest in my soul♪

265
00:22:06,590 --> 00:22:13,726
♪Affection lingers, unforgettable♪

266
00:22:13,726 --> 00:22:18,110
♪Ink-stained scrolls recall bygones♪

267
00:22:18,110 --> 00:22:20,734
♪Each stroke holds a thought♪

